root: ^"Yes, I hope Queen will be happy."

mission: ^The maid acknowledged, accepting the soft plumes from my hands with a brief nod.
^Yet, just as before, she swiftly returned to her tasks, the atmosphere of the castle resonating with the hustle and bustle of daily life.
^The acknowledgment was as fleeting as a passing breeze, lost amid the duties that held the castle in an eternal embrace.
